sentences: Dallas James Koehlke (born 1991), better known by his stage name DallasK, is an American DJ, record producer, writer, artist, and singer based in Los Angeles.

Active since 2010, he co-wrote and produced Fifth Harmony's 5x platinum single, "Work From Home feat Ty Dolla Sign," as well as their singles "Down" and "He Like That..." off of their self titled album.
2014: Burn (Let Your Mind Go) (with KSHMR featuring Luciana)
2011: Spencer & Hill - One Touch Away (DallasK Remix)
2013: T.I., Pharrell, Robin Thicke - Blurred Lines (DallasK Remix)
2018: Justin Caruso featuring Jake Miller - "Don't Know You" (DallasK Remix)
